  "uuid": "c048d988d9b43b42c3f9638f0d0a19e2",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Production Operator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Cut big slabs to size by operating bridge-cutting machines.</li>\n  <li>Operate profiling/polishing machines.</li>\n  <li>Cut and polish sink holes to templates.</li>\n  <li>Grind and polish edges with portable power tools.</li>\n  <li>Color match various types of resin glues to match stones.</li>\n  <li>Seal natural stones such as Granite after fabrication.</li>\n  <li>Self-inspect work upon completion.</li>\n  <li>Cleaning of equipment and workstation after work.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with co-workers, leaders and Production Supervisor to fulfil all job requirements, production and quality standards.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Physically fit and able to carry heavy weight items.</li>\n  <li>Able to do basic mathematical calculations.</li>\n  <li>Able to work in and adjust to varying production timelines.</li>\n  <li>Able to work as a team player and willing to learn.</li>\n  <li>Possess craftsman ability to use portable power tools and hand tools to cut, grind, shape, and polish      various types of stone products.</li>\n  <li>Experience with proper and safe use of tools utilized in fabrication preferred.</li>\n  <li>Can read and work from drawings and diagrams created manually or from a CAD program.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience with CNC machines will be an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge and prior experience of stone surfaces will be an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Working knowledge of the use of different products and solvents such as various types of adhesive glues, acetone, and denatured alcohol used for fabrication will be an advantage.</li>\n</ul>",
